---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro"
---
<Base title="首页 - 企业展示网站">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="hero-title">专注创新解决方案</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">提供专业的核心产品与服务，助力企业数字化转型</p>
        <div class="hero-features">
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon">🚀</div>
            <h3>创新技术</h3>
            <p>采用前沿技术，提供优质解决方案</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon">💼</div>
            <h3>专业团队</h3>
            <p>拥有丰富经验的专业团队</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon">🎯</div>
            <h3>客户至上</h3>
            <p>以客户需求为中心，提供定制化服务</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="products-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">产品中心</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">精选优质产品，满足不同需求</p>
      <div class="products-grid">
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="product-image">
            <img src="/images/product1.jpg" alt="产品1" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 width=%22200%22 height=%22150%22%3E%3Crect fill=%22%23ddd%22 width=%22200%22 height=%22150%22/%3E%3Ctext fill=%22%23999%22 font-family=%22sans-serif%22 font-size=%2214%22 x=%2250%25%22 y=%2250%25%22 text-anchor=%22middle%22 dy=%22.3em%22%3E产品图片%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'">
          </div>
          <div class="product-info">
            <h3>产品名称一</h3>
            <p>高效稳定的核心产品，适用于多种业务场景，提供完善的技术支持。</p>
            <a href="/products" class="product-link">了解更多 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="product-image">
            <img src="/images/product2.jpg" alt="产品2" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 width=%22200%22 height=%22150%22%3E%3Crect fill=%22%23ddd%22 width=%22200%22 height=%22150%22/%3E%3Ctext fill=%22%23999%22 font-family=%22sans-serif%22 font-size=%2214%22 x=%2250%25%22 y=%2250%25%22 text-anchor=%22middle%22 dy=%22.3em%22%3E产品图片%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'">
          </div>
          <div class="product-info">
            <h3>产品名称二</h3>
            <p>智能化管理平台，提升工作效率，降低运营成本，助力企业快速发展。</p>
            <a href="/products" class="product-link">了解更多 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="product-image">
            <img src="/images/product3.jpg" alt="产品3" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 width=%22200%22 height=%22150%22%3E%3Crect fill=%22%23ddd%22 width=%22200%22 height=%22150%22/%3E%3Ctext fill=%22%23999%22 font-family=%22sans-serif%22 font-size=%2214%22 x=%2250%25%22 y=%2250%25%22 text-anchor=%22middle%22 dy=%22.3em%22%3E产品图片%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'">
          </div>
          <div class="product-info">
            <h3>产品名称三</h3>
            <p>安全可靠的数据解决方案，保障企业数据安全，满足合规要求。</p>
            <a href="/products" class="product-link">了解更多 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="product-image">
            <img src="/images/product4.jpg" alt="产品4" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 width=%22200%22 height=%22150%22%3E%3Crect fill=%22%23ddd%22 width=%22200%22 height=%22150%22/%3E%3Ctext fill=%22%23999%22 font-family=%22sans-serif%22 font-size=%2214%22 x=%2250%25%22 y=%2250%25%22 text-anchor=%22middle%22 dy=%22.3em%22%3E产品图片%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'">
          </div>
          <div class="product-info">
            <h3>产品名称四</h3>
            <p>全面的咨询服务，专业团队提供一对一指导，帮助企业实现目标。</p>
            <a href="/products" class="product-link">了解更多 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-top: 3rem;">
        <a href="/products" class="btn btn-primary">查看所有产品</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>